menu "Display support"

config WAVESHARE_C6_LCD_1_47
    bool "Waveshare ESP32-C6-LCD-1.47 router dashboard"
    depends on IDF_TARGET_ESP32C6
    default n
    help
        Enable the onboard 172x320 ST7789 display on the Waveshare
        ESP32-C6-LCD-1.47. The dashboard is status-only because this board
        has no touch controller. GPIO6/7 drive SPI, GPIO14 is CS, GPIO15 is
        DC, GPIO21 is reset, and GPIO22 controls the backlight.

endmenu
